{"tid":1691510,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做乜都比連登仔屌 好心累 你教下我要點做","createTime":"2019-11-03T16:29:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T02:41:51.000Z","uid":315002,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f6d771009db5aee0e25dfb58a7dff88a3e8c69d7","tid":1691510,"uid":315002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T16:29:57.000Z","msg":"乜都唔做<br />\n連登仔:垃圾！港豬！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nig po story文宣 話自己好嬲<br />\n連登仔:偽黃！又唔出嚟 扮曬係黃咁樣 拎光環！ 垃圾！港豬！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n靜靜雞做文宣<br />\n連登仔: 你係咪覺得場運動表面做到好睇就夠？ 又唔出嚟幫手！垃圾！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出到嚟企後面<br />\n連登仔: 和理有撚用？ 又唔敢企前面 出到嚟打卡？ 一啲都幫唔到手 冇撚用！垃圾！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出到嚟 full gear<br />\n連登仔: cosplay撚！ 做唔到嘢企返後面啦 返屋企啦！ 阻住曬！垃圾！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大佬呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係個個都咁大隻㗎嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係個個都有能力上最前㗎嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係個個都識做救護㗎嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><